---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-12 max-w-screen-md mx-auto w-full">
        <header class="mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-[3rem] leading-tight font-headline text-on-surface mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant">Datenschutzerklärung / Data Protection Statement</p>
        </header>

        <div class="font-body text-on-surface-variant space-y-6">
            <section class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8">
                <h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
                <p>
                    The data controller responsible for this website is:<br/><br/>
                    Chair of Natural Language Processing<br/>
                    Julius-Maximilians-Universität Würzburg<br/>
                    Am Hubland, 97074 Würzburg, Germany<br/>
                    Email: <a href="mailto:nlp@uni-wuerzburg.de" class="text-primary hover:underline">nlp@uni-wuerzburg.de</a>
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8">
                <h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">2. What Data We Collect</h2>
                <p>This website is a <strong>static site</strong> hosted on GitHub Pages. We do not operate any tracking, analytics, or cookie systems of our own. We do not collect, store, or process any personal data through this website.</p>
                <p class="mt-3">When you visit this site, your browser may automatically transmit certain technical data (such as IP address, browser type, and the URL requested) to the web server operated by GitHub (GitHub, Inc., San Francisco, CA, USA). This data is processed under GitHub's own privacy policy: <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary hover:underline">GitHub Privacy Statement</a>.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8">
                <h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">3. External Links</h2>
                <p>This site contains links to external websites. We have no control over the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their respective privacy policies.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8">
                <h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>Under the GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, and erase personal data concerning you. As this website collects no personal data, these rights are not typically applicable here. For inquiries, please contact us at <a href="mailto:nlp@uni-wuerzburg.de" class="text-primary hover:underline">nlp@uni-wuerzburg.de</a>.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8">
                <h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">5. Changes to this Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be published on this page. Last updated: April 2026.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
